#
#
#   Dependencies:
#   - ImageMagick
#   - libmicrohttpd
#   - postgresql
#   - json-c
#   - pcre
#                                                                              
#   The database login details must be edited in the Makefile "install:" target
#    
# 
#   Next compile then initialize the database by using
#
#     make install
#
#   A compiled binary is included already, however you can recompile it using
#   
#     make clean
#     make 
#
#
#   After compilation the program can be run as follows
#
#     ./main.out <dbconfig> <portno>
#
#   Example:
#
#     ./main.out "user=khalile dbname=photoshare sslmode=disable" 8888
#
#
#   There are 2 sample accounts preloaded, both with blank passwords
#   - john@smith.com
#   - fred@smith.com
#
#
#   Sample stock imagery came from the following places:
#   - https://unsplash.com/photos/Ki0dpxd3LGc
#   - http://alpha.wallhaven.cc/wallpaper/73148
#   - http://alpha.wallhaven.cc/wallpaper/96282
#   - http://alpha.wallhaven.cc/wallpaper/13681
#   - http://alpha.wallhaven.cc/wallpaper/286132
#   
#   Other imagery are from game-icons.net, and semantic-ui.
#
#
